reviewText: Been a Deon Cole fan for over 20 years. He started back on Def Comedy Jam. This is older an older taping and he's done TV shows and movies since this, so don't let this sleeping crowd fool you! I was LMAO! 5 Stars
I thought his raw talent was hilarious
